Get composite team talent rankings for all teams in a given year

cfbd_team_talent.Rd

Extracts team talent composite as sourced from 247 rankings

cfbd_team_talent(year = NULL, verbose = FALSE)

Arguments

year

(Integer optional): Year 4 digit format (YYYY)
verbose

Logical parameter (TRUE/FALSE, default: FALSE) to return warnings and messages from function

Source

https://api.collegefootballdata.com/talent

Value

cfbd_team_talent() - A data frame with 3 variables:

year: integer.

Season for the talent rating.

school: character.

Team name.

talent: double.

Overall roster talent points (as determined by 247Sports).

Examples

cfbd_team_talent()
